# Marketing UI

See [src/components/marketing/AGENTS.md](../../src/components/marketing/AGENTS.md) and [docs/DESIGN.md](../../docs/DESIGN.md).

## Section structure

```tsx
<MarketingSection tone="light" headingId="section-heading">
  <MarketingSectionHeader titleId="section-heading" title="..." lead="..." />
  {/* content */}
</MarketingSection>
```

## Padding

Use `py` on `MarketingSection`: `default` | `hero` | `compact` | `spacious` — do not invent custom `py` values.

## Dark bands

- Standard dark: `tone="dark"` → `background.dark`
- Finale CTA: `tone="darkAccent"` → `primary.dark`
- Body on dark: `color="grey.300"` for muted text
- CTA: `InvertedButton`

## Typography variants

`marketingHeroTitle`, `marketingSectionTitle`, `marketingFeatureTitle`, `marketingLead`, `marketingStat` only.
